        compares the text of expected table cell with the actual table cell text of a table with from a table element
        Parameters:
        type - - the locator type e.g. Locator.id, Locator.xpath
        locator - - the locator string e.g. login, //input[@id='login']
        elementMatch - - if there are multiple matches of the selector, this is which match (starting at 0) to interact with
        row - - the number of the row in the table - note, row numbering starts at 1, NOT 0
        col - - the number of the column in the table - note, column numbering starts at 1, NOT 0
        text - - what text do we expect to be in the table cell
        Returns:
        Integer: 1 if a failure and 0 if a pass
